00:36:47,126 --> 00:36:48,290
I hear it.

506
00:36:49,646 --> 00:36:50,707
Mr. President?

507
00:36:56,374 --> 00:36:57,688
Okay, I'll speak the truth.

508
00:36:59,999 --> 00:37:01,050
I don't trust you.

509
00:37:02,196 --> 00:37:03,698
I don't trust your countries.

510
00:37:04,900 --> 00:37:06,655
I don't understand
your cultures.

511
00:37:07,181 --> 00:37:09,913
I'm afraid of you.
That's why we build the bombs.

512
00:37:10,243 --> 00:37:13,389
Right now, you're proving that all
my fears are... are well-founded.

513
00:37:14,136 --> 00:37:15,666
I tell myself I should have no...

514
00:37:16,103 --> 00:37:17,709
no prejudices, but I do.

515
00:37:18,453 --> 00:37:19,493
We all do.

516
00:37:20,229 --> 00:37:21,807
We are no different from you.

517
00:37:22,512 --> 00:37:25,066
Let them hear it.
Let them all hear it.

518
00:37:28,726 --> 00:37:29,759
We're all the same.

519
00:37:30,528 --> 00:37:31,627
We're all the same!

520
00:37:35,158 --> 00:37:38,024
Everything is... connected.

521
00:37:38,379 --> 00:37:39,505
Everything is...

522
00:37:41,800 --> 00:37:42,861
connected.

523
00:37:46,044 --> 00:37:47,631
We all want the same things,

524
00:37:48,107 --> 00:37:49,788
and we're all afraid
of losing them.

525
00:37:50,598 --> 00:37:52,185
That's become our commonality...

526
00:37:53,387 --> 00:37:54,410
Fear.

527
00:37:56,381 --> 00:37:58,259
We imagine fearsome Gods,

528
00:37:59,176 --> 00:38:00,894
and we build fearsome weapons.

529
00:38:01,908 --> 00:38:03,354
We're lost to fear.

530
00:38:06,819 --> 00:38:08,199
- We must...
- Stop...

531
00:38:08,894 --> 00:38:09,946
...stop.

532
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:13,731
The fear must...

533
00:38:15,121 --> 00:38:16,182
...must stop.

534
00:38:54,183 --> 00:38:55,836
I give the order to stand down.

535
00:39:04,028 --> 00:39:05,239
Is anyone listening?

536
00:39:10,254 --> 00:39:11,268
What was that?

537
00:39:14,554 --> 00:39:15,991
I can understand you!

538
00:39:20,046 --> 00:39:21,905
<i>How is this possible...</i>

539
00:39:41,002 --> 00:39:42,054
Oh, my God.

540
00:40:36,554 --> 00:40:38,423
<i>We've been
given a choice today...</i>

541
00:40:39,291 --> 00:40:41,225
<i>a choice to listen to each other</i>

542
00:40:42,439 --> 00:40:44,335
<i>and hear the heart
of humanity...</i>

543
00:40:45,885 --> 00:40:48,411
<i>A choice to change things
by ourselves,</i>

544
00:40:49,055 --> 00:40:50,266
<i>for ourselves...</i>

545
00:40:50,749 --> 00:40:52,773
<i>...in the knowledge
that we are not alone.</i>

546
00:41:06,555 --> 00:41:07,973
